headline: Ulta Beauty (ULTA) Valuation Check As Major Brand Launches Expand Its Retail Portfolio
summary: Ulta Beauty (ULTA) is drawing fresh attention after hosting several high profile brand launches, including Rare Beauty’s record breaking debut at the retailer, along with new partnerships with Stripes Beauty and Lemme x Kylie Cosmetics. See our latest analysis for Ulta Beauty. These high profile launches and store openings sit alongside a strong run in the shares, with a 90 day share price return of 29.05% and a 1 year total shareholder return of 64.57%, which points to solid positive...
